        config
        widgetsaddons
        completion
        coreaddons
        guiaddons

        windowsystem

        required components
        core
        gui
        widgets

        network
        printsupport

find_package(python 3.8 required components interpreter optional_components development)

libs.content:
find_library (opencolorio_library
    names
        opencolorio
        opencolorio_${cmake_match_1}_${cmake_match_2}
        opencolorio${cmake_match_1}
    hints
        ${opencolorio_library_path}
        env opencolorio_library_path
    paths
        /usr/lib64
        /usr/local/lib64
        /sw/lib
        /opt/local/lib
    doc "the ocio library")

find_library(quazip_libraries
			win32_debug_postfix d
            names quazip5
			hints /usr/lib /usr/lib64
		)

find_library(vpx_libraries
	names vpx vpxmd
	hints _vpx_root_paths
	path_suffixes bin lib lib/win32
)
